data.description: Discover your new haven in this expansive residence featuring a master suite on the main floor. Ideally situated just a few miles from SeaWorld, Fiesta Texas, UTSA, Valero Trails, La Cantera Mall, and Lackland Air Force Base, this stunning two-story home boasts a spacious layout with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and an expansive living area on the second floor. Enjoy numerous upgrades, including newly renovated windows, a modernized kitchen, and a delightful playground. Welcome to your new home-feel free to share your thoughts. Thank you.
